OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775837470
OL,3,CEurotunnel fined #2.5m after heavy
OL,4,Clighting carriage fell on surveyor
OL,6,FEurotunnel has been fined #2.25
OL,7,Fmillion after an 115kg lighting
OL,8,Fcarriage fell on a surveyor and
OL,9,Fseriously injured them in an "entirely
OL,10,Fpreventable" incident.
OL,12,FThe worker was standing at the bottom
OL,13,Fof a lighting mast as a carriage was
OL,14,Fbeing winched 18 metres in the air
OL,15,Fduring an inspection at Eurotunnel's
OL,16,FUK terminal in Folkestone, on 5 April
OL,17,F2018.
OL,19,FThe wires holding it failed and the
OL,20,Flighting carriage fell, striking the
OL,21,Fsurveyor.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@LO]
